name: AI Art Imitating Pablo Picasso Inspired By The Great Alfred Prufrock Poem - Genesis Edition

metadata.name: AI Art Imitating Pablo Picasso Inspired By The Great Alfred Prufrock Poem - Genesis Edition
metadata.description:
What if AI painted the words of T.S. Eliot poem The Love Song of J. Alfred Prufrock while imitating the style of Pablo Picasso? This totally amazing AI art collection answers that question. So these images are a combination of classical masterpieces by Pablo Picasso and AI art, as Picasso's paintings are juxtaposed against artificial intelligence images. So you can see the greatness of the painter and the AI attempt to imitate it.

This is the super rare Genesis Edition. It contains the first 200 AI art NFTs ever minted in this collection. So it's likely to become the most rare and most valuable edition in this totally amazing AI art collection inspired by that great T.S. Eliot poem.
